<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Nuevo Contrato Embajador - WAPPY LTDA</title>
  <style>
    body { margin:0; padding:0; background:#f4f7f4; font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,sans-serif; color:#1a2e1a; }
    .wrapper { width:100%; background:#f4f7f4; padding:36px 0; }
    .card { max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid #d4e8d4; box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.07); }
    .header { background:#166435; padding:28px 32px 24px; text-align:center; }
    .header h1 { margin:0; font-size:20px; color:#ffffff; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-.02em; }
    .header p { margin:8px 0 0; font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,.75); }
    .badge { display:inline-block; background:rgba(255,255,255,.15); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3); color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.08em; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:20px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-top:10px; }
    .body { padding:28px 32px; }
    .alert-box { background:#f0fdf4; border-left:4px solid #22c55e; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0; padding:14px 18px; margin-bottom:24px; font-size:14px; color:#166435; font-weight:600; }
    .section-title { font-size:11px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em; color:#5a8a5a; margin:20px 0 10px; border-bottom:1px solid #e4f0e4; padding-bottom:6px; }
    .data-table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; }
    .data-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background:#f8fbf8; }
    .data-table td { padding:9px 12px; font-size:13.5px; border-bottom:1px solid #edf4ed; vertical-align:top; }
    .data-table td:first-child { font-weight:600; color:#2d5a2d; width:40%; }
    .data-table td:last-child { color:#1a2e1a; }
    .id-box { background:#f0fdf4; border:2px dashed #22c55e; border-radius:10px; padding:14px 18px; text-align:center; margin:20px 0; }
    .id-box span { font-size:18px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.12em; color:#166435; font-family:'Courier New',monospace; }
    .id-box p { margin:4px 0 0; font-size:12px; color:#5a8a5a; }
    .footer { background:#f0fdf4; border-top:1px solid #d4e8d4; padding:18px 32px; text-align:center; font-size:12px; color:#5a8a5a; }
    .footer strong { color:#166435; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>🖊️ Nuevo Contrato Firmado</h1>
        <p>Un embajador acaba de completar y firmar su contrato</p>
        <span class="badge">Notificación Admin</span>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="alert-box">✅ Contrato firmado electrónicamente — acción requerida: verificar documentos adjuntos.</div>

        <div class="id-box">
          <span>{{contractId}}</span>
          <p>ID de Contrato</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section-title">📋 Datos Personales</div>
        <table class="data-table">
          <tr><td>Nombre</td><td>{{nombre}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Cédula</td><td>{{cedula}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Lugar de Expedición</td><td>{{expedicion}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Correo</td><td>{{email}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Celular</td><td>{{celular}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Dirección</td><td>{{direccion}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Domicilio</td><td>{{domicilio}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Profesión</td><td>{{profesion}}</td></tr>
        </table>

        <div class="section-title">🗺️ Territorio</div>
        <table class="data-table">
          <tr><td>Territorio Asignado</td><td>{{territorio}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Municipios Aledaños</td><td>{{aledanos}}</td></tr>
        </table>

        <div class="section-title">🏦 Información Bancaria</div>
        <table class="data-table">
          <tr><td>Banco</td><td>{{banco}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Tipo de Cuenta</td><td>{{tipoCuenta}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Número de Cuenta</td><td>{{numeroCuenta}}</td></tr>
        </table>

        <div class="section-title">📎 Documentos Cargados</div>
        <table class="data-table">
          <tr><td>Documentos</td><td>{{documentos}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Fecha de Firma</td><td>{{fechaFirma}}</td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <strong>WAPPY LTDA</strong> — NIT 901437310 — soporte@wappy.club<br>
        Este es un mensaje automático del sistema de embajadores.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
